Texas Flip and Move - Season 1, Episode 3




Glam Cabin vs. Rooster Reno

A house on Foster Drive in Lake Worth, Texas, is a quaint stone-clad house with a small addition. Both the Slays and Randy like it. The Slays think it will make a nice hunting cabin while Randy believes he can make money just selling the stone.
